      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Body Text 10pt  space banda"><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Motion-Law</text><text styleclass="Body Text 10pt  space banda" translate="true">: the name of the mathematical function that we apply for each segment. The name is derived from the </text></para>
          <list id="0" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#183;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Body Text 10pt  space banda" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:10pt; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="Body Text 10pt  space banda"><text styleclass="Body Text 10pt  space banda" translate="true">Shape of the Acceleration graph - e.g. Modified Trapezoid</text></li>
          </list>
          <list id="1" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#183;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Popup Box" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:10pt; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">Mathematical definition - e.g. Triple Harmonic, Cubic</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">Motion function - e.g. Constant-Velocity, Dwell</text></li>
          </list>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">The mathematical function is based on either Polynomial or Harmonic.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text 10pt  space banda"><text styleclass="Body Text 10pt  space banda" translate="true">Each </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Motion-Law</text><text styleclass="Body Text 10pt  space banda" translate="true"> has advantages and disadvantages. Thus, you should select a </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Motion-Law</text><text styleclass="Body Text 10pt  space banda" translate="true"> for the application.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text 10pt  space banda"><text styleclass="Body Text 10pt  space banda" translate="true">Other terms for </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Motion-Law</text><text styleclass="Body Text 10pt  space banda" translate="true"> are: </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Cam-Law</text><text styleclass="Body Text 10pt  space banda" translate="true"> or </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Segment Type</text><text styleclass="Popup Box2" translate="true">. </text></para>
